{"tid":1332640,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKBU]浸大moodle被hack bu人快啲入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-19T11:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:37:51.000Z","uid":56902,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d59f11d77d6527b097862d3bcd6cbeb9af3c4c58","tid":1332640,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"我想約略統計下有幾多同學比人偷咗個人資料，所有bu同學請喺#2投票<br />\n<br />\n如果比人偷咗資料，會收到兩封email（一封Dear(你個名），大約講你被人偷咗資料；另一封係To all students)<br />\n請喺#2比正評<br />\n<br />\n如果只係收到To all students個封嘅就喺#2比負評<br />\n<br />\n轉載浸大編委報道：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/423763107707890/posts/2243933455690837/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F423763107707890%2Fposts%2F2243933455690837%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMVx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=a36695ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/423763107707890/posts/2243933455690837/</a><br />\n<br />\n網上教學平台遭黑客入侵 學生資料被盜取<br />\n<br />\n【浸大編委訊】今日（19日）校方透過群發電郵向學生表示於7月15、16日，Moodle（網上教學平台）系統遭駭客入侵，部分學生的個人資料包括姓名、電郵及相片等被盜取。校方並沒有公布受害學生數目，只是稱將按程序處理，並呼籲同學注意網絡安全。<br />\n<br />\n而有部分資料被外洩的同學告知本會，校方以電郵方式通知他們的個人資料被惡意竊取。據了解，受害者包括50屆幹事會全體成員、學生自發組織浸大山神發言人陳樂行及其骨幹成員，以及浸大社關成員。 而暫時未有任何現屆學生會（包括本會、評議會及幹事會）成員被告知其資料被偷竊。<br />\n<br />\n本會在此呼籲同學勤更改所有帳戶密碼及清理網上足跡，以免被壞人有機可乘，偷取資料。"},{"pid":"f6f699cc814d49649473b07d46f603abada8864c","tid":1332640,"uid":56902,"like":66,"dislike":74,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"如果比人偷咗資料，會收到兩封email（一封Dear(你個名），大約講你被人偷咗資料；另一封係To all students)<br />\n請喺呢個留言比正評<br />\n<br />\n如果只係收到To all students個封嘅就喺呢個留言比負評"},{"pid":"88865eeae666bb352108e2aeb4c82c516b4ac9d4","tid":1332640,"uid":213819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推 封信基本上咩都無講"},{"pid":"8c6e8403674e9d849ddf55257969f41c754a92cf","tid":1332640,"uid":14906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9989020d624286639de18de75d92002e16663a67","tid":1332640,"uid":66527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"又多一個唔讀bu既理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd7858cf194ce4b30a4de283ab6527680008f40","tid":1332640,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"睇樣淨係hack 莊？"},{"pid":"570dae1e0ad7b745983243c55d5692cad49f25f4","tid":1332640,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"浸中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccfce15585d840f792924b23a8be2f866feb877","tid":1332640,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"浸中cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089eaff85c846a7e002938644e920dbee009982f","tid":1332640,"uid":270009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"Cls 我grad咗都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾學校出賣學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ec890c7a922c669355f0b53c5c58f99120c18a","tid":1332640,"uid":26893,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9fd7858cf194ce4b30a4de283ab6527680008f40","tid":1332640,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"睇樣淨係hack 莊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"發夢見到我同好多friend都俾人hack咗 我幾乎咩都冇參加既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f031093ba9f7d535e6ccb163734b104d79df96d3","tid":1332640,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"讀書唔叻先要讀BU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9080e695acc732c22692fed6f649c4f0b8de29ea","tid":1332640,"uid":120263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:51:30.000Z","msg":"cls 中左 點搞"},{"pid":"541e1ed6da7a44787ae63e0969a10c3fd80b46c3","tid":1332640,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd7858cf194ce4b30a4de283ab6527680008f40","tid":1332640,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"睇樣淨係hack 莊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"轉載至山神fb<br />\n<br />\n1900 有同學打畀HKBU ITO查詢，整理詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n實際上只有同學X帳戶被盜用，但被盜帳號可以透過Moodle系統都可以檢閱同班同學資料，例如同一個course 但唔同section嘅同學資料，因此牽連到唔少同學都收到電郵，代表因同學X帳戶被盜用而已取得同學姓名、電郵、相片等資料。<br />\n<br />\n至於「forum post」係指 moodle入面嘅forum 功能，因甚少人用，影響不大。<br />\n<br />\nITO有嘗試聯絡X同學，但未有回覆 ，因此唔肯定同香港最近發生嘅事有無關係，<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n被人偷咗資料嘅人嘅共通點：有同同學X上過堂<br />\n所以未必關莊事"},{"pid":"2f84b083a0c510c6a705df707ff675f75693a9e5","tid":1332640,"uid":238704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"屌， grad咗都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b8eaeea755af38842507ff7840bd9a150b319d","tid":1332640,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"推番上去畀更多人見到同投票<br />\n<br />\nbtw721見"},{"pid":"bce2cd1b1c2a798788f02d7ff0c3f3a3afdad0a8","tid":1332640,"uid":1851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"牽連應該好廣 因為moodle好似可以睇返曬4年讀過啲咩course 咁搞法都睇到幾撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4bc958be1cfe27e8ee10ca571e668c10f97f06","tid":1332640,"uid":259373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"我都中咗<br />\n推"},{"pid":"efd259dfd654564b1d06bd52f0e87ba71bf736a7","tid":1332